<section id="about" class="section about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="about-intro">
          I'm a data engineer based in Amsterdam with a passion for building robust,
          scalable data systems.
        </p>
        <p>
          I studied computer science, where I was fascinated by distributed systems,
          data streams, and blockchain programming. This fascination led me to dive
          deep into all things related to blockchain and data engineering.
        </p>
        <p>
          I fell in love with learning new things related to emerging technologies.
          Whether it's designing fault-tolerant architectures, implementing smart
          contracts, or optimizing data pipelines, I enjoy tackling complex technical
          challenges.
        </p>
        <p>
          I also like to work on my own projects, continuously exploring new tools
          and technologies to expand my skill set.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <div class="highlight-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
              <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/>
              <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Data Engineering</h3>
          <p>Building scalable pipelines and architectures that handle complex data workflows</p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <div class="highlight-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Blockchain</h3>
          <p>Smart contract development, DeFi protocols, and blockchain forensics</p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <div class="highlight-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
